Author: denisw
Title: [ANN] Assetron Energy ICO - P2P Crowdfunding Platform for Clean Energy Projects
Body: ASSETRON ENERGY are developing a decentralized P2P Investment Platform for Renewable Energy Projects  — connecting investors with clean energy projects in need of financing.  To supercharge the supply of clean energy demands of communities and businesses around the world, our Blockchain Powered Platform, will enable ASSETRON Token holders the opportunity to co-invest into green energy projects and receive revenue based on the proportion of the investment.  Essentially the key mission is to bridge the gap between energy consumers who will greatly benefit from a renewable energy setup, but can not afford to do so upfront, and socially conscious investors, who understand the benefits of investing into renewable energy, but don’t have an easy avenue to do so.  Assetron Energy will not only utilise the funds gained from the Token Sale to develop their platform, but also in what is believed to be a first in the cryptocurrency history, use part of the funds to commission a 1MW Solar Plant in Australia, setting a new precedent for the potential of cryptocurrency. This will be the life spark of Assetron Energy — the consistent income the plant will generate will ensure that we continue to have funding for as long as 25–30 years, giving the longevity to the company long past the end of the ICO.[/center]   SOFT CAP REACHED - OVER 200,000 USD Raised  Be part of a ICO that will make renewable energy affordable to everyone  Buy ASTRN Tokens now! https://assetron.energy   Latest Press Release: https://medium.com/assetron/press-release-16-10-2017-5218e2f4b9d0  Roadmap  WE ARE In Week 2 - $0.034 USD (Final week Token price will be set at $0.04)   WHAT ARE ASSETRON(ASTRN) TOKENS ASSETRON (ASTRN) Tokens will be the primary currency used on the Assetron Energy Investments Platform, which will be utilised by users to co-invest into various renewable energy projects and receive revenue from those projects in ASTRN Tokens. As the Tokens will sit on the Waves Platform, users will be able to instantly exchange between ASTRN, other cryptocurrency and fiat currencies on the Waves Decentralized Exchange. Partners Wild Environmental - http://www.wildenvironmental.com/ Token Sale Details Token Sale Period: Pre-sale + 4 Weeks   Week 1 20/11/2017 : $0.031 USD Week 2 27/11/2017: $0.034 USD Week 3 04/12/2017 : $0.038 USD Week 4 11/12/2017 : $0.040 USD  ACCEPTING BTC, ETH, LTC and WAVES   Cost of 1 ASSETRON    BUY TOKENS HERE https://tokensale.assetron.energy/address/   Assetron Energy Referral Programme  Four Simple Steps to get rewarded with free ASTRN Tokens  1) Refer friends to our website @ https://assetron.energy 2) Give them your Waves Wallet Address 3) They contribute and enter your Waves Address in the purchase form 4) You and your friend get 20% bonus ASTRN Tokens!     Bounty  10,000,000 ASSETRON (ASTRN) Tokens have been allocated for the Token Sale  The bounty campaign will feature the following  •   White Paper Translations - 1,500,000 ASTRN      o   Russian - 150,000 ASTRN - DONE      o   Hindi - 150,000 ASTRN - DONE       o   Portuguese - 150,000 ASTRN       o   Mandarin - 150,000 ASTRN       o   Korean - 150,000 ASTRN       o   Arabic - 150,000 ASTRN - DONE       o   French - 150,000 ASTRN       o   Japanese - 150,000 ASTRN       o   Indonesian - 150,000 ASTRN - DONE       o   Spanish - 150,000 ASTRN •   Facebook Campaign - 1,500,000 ASTRN https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdVBLiLSvj0H-UWvJbuI_H_08bhM147875UgzYO1Gvzag5Giw/viewform?usp=sf_link •   Twitter Campaign - 1,500,000 ASTRN •   Medium Articles - 1,500,000 ASTRN •   BitcoinTalk Reviews - 1,500,000 ASTRN •   Personal Blog Reviews (Must have own domain) - 1,500,000 ASTRN •   Miscellaneous Rewards- 1,000,000 ASTRN  To receive their share of Bounty Tokens, all participants will need to send proof of work and their waves wallet address to bounty@assetron.energy  All Bounty Tokens will be distributed after the sale. Author: denisw
Title: [ANN] Assetron Energy ICO - P2P Crowdfunding Platform for Clean Energy Projects
Body: Hi. Thank you for your comment. Everyone is entitled to their opinion, whatever it may be.  This is far from a scam, we are a real company based in Sydney. The Token Sale is run strictly under Australian law.  Although we are a small startup, we have clear goals in mind and solid team to back them up.  Our main goal is to enable anyone in the world the ability to generate their own renewable energy affordably and at the same time providing a safe and stable investment opportunity. All that utilising cryptocurrency for the benefit of transparency, security and low operational costs.  If your not into that sort of thing - definitely keep your coins to yourself. We only want people who have the same beliefs  as us to support our mission and project.
